" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Primary syphilis: Penile chancre",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 203px; height: 306px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    A chancre due to syphilis is an ulcerative lesion that is often painless and has an indurated character. Chancres arise at the site of initial inoculation of the organism.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
